= SAGA job adaptor for DRMAA compilant systems =

== Installation ==
Make sure that SAGA_LOCATION environment variable is set. Then type::

  make
  sudo make install
  
== Configuration ==
Edit the ``ogf_drmaa_job_adaptor.ini`` configuration file and update the ``drmaa_path`` property. 

== Running ==
This adapter handles the following URL schemas:
* none
* any://
* drmaa://